# - Config file for the dpp package
# It defines the following variables
#  dpp_INCLUDE_DIRS - include directories for dpp
#  dpp_LIBRARY      - libraries to link against
#  dpp_LIBRARIES    - libraries to link against
#  dpp_WITH_BIO     - flag for Boost/Serialization I/O DLL (a.k.a. 'bio')
#  dpp_BIO_LIBRARY  - library targets to link against (Boost I/O library)
#  dpp_WITH_REFLECTION  - flag for reflection DLL
#  dpp_REFLECTION_LIBRARY - library targets to link against (reflection library)

